# 技術スタック
## コア技術
- Python ^3.12
- TCOD ^16.2.3
- tcod-ecs ^5.2.3 (Entity Component System)
- pytest (Testing)
- black (Formatter)
- mypy (Type Checker)
- flake8 (Linter)
- poetry (Package Manager)

## プロジェクト構造

Project directory structure:

src/roguelike/
├── core/           # Core systems
├── game/           # Game logic
├── world/          # Game world
│   ├── map/        # Map generation
│   ├── entity/     # Entities
│   └── spawner/    # Spawner
├── ui/             # User interface
│   ├── screens/    # Screens
│   └── handlers/   # Input handlers
└── data/           # Data
